Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.48,0:00:18.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,我以为这个时候我已经会习惯了死亡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I thought I'd be used to death by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.32,0:00:22.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,八条命跟在大冰封中死去的七十亿人比起来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's eight lives against the seven billion
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.03,0:00:23.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,算得了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}we lost in the Freeze?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.41,0:00:27.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,但这样不同\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But it's different this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.91,0:00:30.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,这不是因为严寒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This isn't the Cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.21,0:00:32.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,是因为我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.79,0:00:34.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}People.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.84,0:00:38.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,互相残暴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Wasting each other to violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.76,0:00:40.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,停不下来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And we can't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.84,0:00:44.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们对一切的答案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's our answer for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.93,0:00:47.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们迷失在其中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We get lost in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.43,0:00:51.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,我迷失在其中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I got lost in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.52,0:00:53.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,但现在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But now...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.02,0:00:57.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,我只想要这一切能停下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All I want is for it to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.13,0:01:16.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,我只想要有一个我能闭上双眼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I want just one night where I close my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.80,0:01:19.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,不害怕另一边的夜晚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and I'm not afraid of what's on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.34,0:01:23.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,一个我不感到孤单的夜晚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}One night where I don't feel so alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.59,0:01:28.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,在雪国列车上  1034节车厢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}On Snowpiercer, 1,034 cars long.
