Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.82,0:01:47.54,特效,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\a6\c&H020202&\fs24\fn方正兰亭准黑_GBK\fsp8\t(\fsp11)\pos(192,166)}{\fsp3\t(\fsp4.125)}第二季 第七{\fsp0}集\N{\fsp3\t(\fsp4.125)}"解答一切{\fsp0}"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.84,0:02:01.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,儿子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My son.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.30,0:02:05.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,主在绝望之时会守护我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The Lord is watching over us in times of despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.51,0:02:07.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,损失在所难免\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Loss comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.85,0:02:10.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,威尔福德知道怎么攻击我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Wilford knew exactly how to hit us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.18,0:02:12.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,他在这边肯定有内应\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He has to have someone over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.98,0:02:16.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,一个告诉了他这边紧张局势的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Someone who told him about the tensions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.65,0:02:18.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,人们会责怪车尾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}People are gonna blame the Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.73,0:02:20.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,我得弥补这事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I have to make this right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.44,0:02:22.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们都需要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We both do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.65,0:02:25.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,你证明不是车尾干的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You prove it wasn't the Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.57,0:02:27.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,与此同时我会防止事态失控\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll keep a lid on things while you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.92,0:02:38.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,大爱丽丝边境封锁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Big Alice border is on lockdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:40.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,我在每个连接处都派了司闸员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I've got Brakemen on every link.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.00,0:02:42.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,目前没有问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's no trouble yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.17,0:02:43.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,迟早会有的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's just a matter of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:45.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  这事会发酵的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah. This is gonna boil.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.72,0:02:54.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,司闸员博斯科维奇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Breachman Boscovic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.64,0:02:57.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,你的损失也是雪国列车的损失\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your loss is all of Snowpiercer's.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.27,0:02:59.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,你知道是谁干的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know who did this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.11,0:03:01.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,我向你保证不是车尾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I promise you, it wasn't the Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.65,0:03:05.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,请你远离他们  立刻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Please get away from them. Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.03,0:03:11.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.37,0:03:13.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,交给我吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Leave this with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.96,0:03:21.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,拿着  是圣克里斯多福\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Here. It's Saint Christopher.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.00,0:03:24.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,可以保护你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}For protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.76,0:03:32.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,我会帮你看着他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll keep an eye on him for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.64,0:03:33.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,我保证\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.47,0:03:36.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,他忙完这边后  我会带他去茶室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}When he's finished here, I'll take him to the Tea Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.56,0:03:37.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  牧师\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thank you, Pastor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.53,0:03:50.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,你不能这样涂抹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey! You can't smear it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.28,0:03:52.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是蛇形运动  拜托\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's a snaking motion. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.58,0:03:54.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,血还多着呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's a lot more blood where that came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.42,0:03:59.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,警探\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.17,0:04:01.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,要处理的案子好多啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Wow, what a caseload.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.84,0:04:02.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,我需要你的帮助\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Could use your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.92,0:04:04.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,是车尾人干的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The Tailies did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.42,0:04:05.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,就算不是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And even if they didn't,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.26,0:04:06.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,像以前那样嫁祸给他们就行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}just pin it on them like you used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.72,0:04:09.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,别烦她  她度过了艰难的一晚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oi. Give her a break. She had a rough night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.55,0:04:11.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,你需要什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What do you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.43,0:04:14.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,我在那边的地板上发现了这个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I found this over there on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.60,0:04:15.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,复古威尔福德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's vintage Wilford.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.97,0:04:17.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,老式字样的W\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Old style W.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.77,0:04:19.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,你有见过吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You ever see one before?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.02,0:04:20.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,或许在头等厢里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Maybe up in First?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.73,0:04:22.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.73,0:04:24.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,你根本没看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You didn't even look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.66,0:04:27.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,还是没见过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh. Still no.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.61,0:04:30.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,算了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.24,0:04:38.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,我认识一个或许能帮上忙的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know someone who might be able to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.25,0:04:40.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.00,0:04:41.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,一个叫卡佳的女人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This woman, Katya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.04,0:04:42.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,她有一个卧铺包厢  里面全是古董\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She has a couchette full of vintage stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.46,0:04:45.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,带我去吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Wanna take me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.80,0:04:47.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.30,0:04:51.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,她当时跟他站在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She was standing right there with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.01,0:04:52.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,在边境对面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Across the border.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:54.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,我听不清  但看上去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I couldn't hear much, but it looked like
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.05,0:04:55.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,他像是在给她一个选择\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}he was offering her a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.35,0:04:56.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,她选择留下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She chose to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.77,0:04:57.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,看上去是这样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's what it looked like.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.93,0:04:59.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,但我不知道她的动机\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But I cannot know her motives.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.60,0:05:01.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,派奥德丽过去本身就有风险\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It was a risk sending Audrey over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.23,0:05:04.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,她是过去替你执行任务的  不是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, she was there on a mission for you, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.15,0:05:05.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,-她完成了吗  -没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Did she complete it? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.36,0:05:07.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们还是没法监听到他们的通讯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We still don't have access to their comms.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.19,0:05:09.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,也许她只是留在那完成任务\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So maybe she just stayed behind to finish the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.32,0:05:12.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,不管怎样  她是奥德丽小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, either way, she's Miss Audrey,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.66,0:05:14.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,夜车地位最高的女性\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Doyenne of the Nightcar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.24,0:05:15.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,她是我们的一员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She's one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.41,0:05:17.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,看上去就是变节  即使真相并非如此\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Looks like a defection even if it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.79,0:05:26.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,*太阳为何...*\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}* Why does the sun... *
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.25,0:05:28.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,大爱丽丝  大爱丽丝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Big Alice, Big Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.67,0:05:30.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,雪国列车致以问候  请回复\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good day from Snowpiercer. Come in...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:34.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,*海水为何匆匆拍向海岸*\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}* Why does the sea rush to shore? *
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.43,0:05:37.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,大爱丽丝  雪国列车呼叫大爱丽丝  请回复\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Big Alice, Big Alice. Snowpiercer calling. Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.76,0:05:38.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,快接听  大爱丽丝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Pick up, Big Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.77,0:05:41.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你在听  你这个变态的臭老头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know you're listening, you psychotic old goat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.60,0:05:46.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,你好  本  你好像很需要人关注\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hello, Ben. You sound needy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.11,0:05:50.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们今晚将到达喜马拉雅山环形路\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're going to be hitting the Himalaya Roundabout tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.99,0:05:51.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,大事件啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Big event.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.86,0:05:56.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们要回去接你们勇敢的首领  梅兰妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're turning back for your brave chief, Melanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.83,0:05:58.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们想和奥德丽说话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We want to speak with Audrey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:06:00.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,瞧谁又去我的火车头了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ah, look who's in my Engine again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.91,0:06:03.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,奥德丽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Audrey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.50,0:06:05.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,是莱顿大王\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's King Layton.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.34,0:06:08.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,来接听\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Collect.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.09,0:06:10.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,她在泡澡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She's been in the tub.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.55,0:06:11.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,心情不太好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Bit of a mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.63,0:06:14.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,昨晚那些响声是怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What was all that noise last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.38,0:06:15.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,警报声  边境封锁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Alarms, sealed borders.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.89,0:06:17.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,遇到麻烦了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Some kind of trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.22,0:06:19.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们列车上有些骚乱而已\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just a little domestic unrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.72,0:06:21.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,但你肯定对此毫不知情  对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But you wouldn't know anything about that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.60,0:06:23.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,稍等  先生们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}One sec, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.06,0:06:27.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,她来了  迷人但怒气冲冲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Here she comes, fetching but grumpy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.06,0:06:29.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,你好  莱顿  我来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hello, Layton. I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.57,0:06:30.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,你错过了宵禁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You missed curfew.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.49,0:06:35.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,我这人一向有点叛逆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, uh, I've always been a bit of a rebel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.03,0:06:38.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.03,0:06:42.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,他想知道我是否强迫你留在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He wants to know if I'm holding you against your will.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.33,0:06:46.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,我没事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.34,0:06:50.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想  我们准备好打开边境门  让你回来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're ready to open the border for you if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.05,0:06:59.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,先不要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.35,0:07:01.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,你确定吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.98,0:07:06.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,这还不够好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.23,0:07:11.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,她是在铤而走险\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She's walking the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.44,0:07:15.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,或者她刚被睡完  正在玫瑰水里泡澡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Or she's freshly shagged, bathing in rosewater.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.82,0:07:19.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须假设她的身份暴露了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We have to assume that she's been compromised.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.82,0:07:21.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah. We do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.17,0:07:36.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,你有没有听到关于雪国列车的消息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Have you heard anything about Snowpiercer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.55,0:07:39.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,警报响了一整晚  没人知道发生了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The alarms went off all night. No one knows what's happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.93,0:07:42.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,威尔福德把自己和奥德丽锁在车头里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Wilford has locked himself in the Engine with Audrey,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.31,0:07:43.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,我被拒之门外\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and I have been shut out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.77,0:07:46.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,有人受到伤害了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Has anyone...been hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.60,0:07:49.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,你的澳大利亚人一定没事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm sure that your Aussie is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.73,0:07:54.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们要袭击我们吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Are they going to attack us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.86,0:07:57.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,艾莉克斯  我们该担心吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Alex. Should we be worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.24,0:07:58.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,我去弄清楚怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm gonna find out what's happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.45,0:07:59.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:01.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,赛克斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sykes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.49,0:08:02.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,等一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.12,0:08:04.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,到底怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.41,0:08:06.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,是我们干的  对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This was us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.54,0:08:08.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果威尔福德没告诉你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If Wilford didn't tell you,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.79,0:08:10.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,那你就无权知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}then you're not supposed to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.25,0:08:13.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.67,0:08:14.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.21,0:08:16.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,你去问他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Take it up with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.27,0:08:27.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,三等厢的情况越来越糟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's getting bad in Third.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.98,0:08:30.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们都认为是我们杀了维修工\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They all think we killed the Breachman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.15,0:08:31.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,反正我们待在这里很安全\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, well, we're safe back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.40,0:08:32.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以关上这边的门\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We can close our own doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.44,0:08:34.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们在前车的同伴怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What about all our people uptrain?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.19,0:08:35.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,莱茨和温妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Lights and Winnie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.36,0:08:36.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.69,0:08:39.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,你的英语能力逐渐恢复了  大力士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}See, your English is coming back, Strong Boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.90,0:08:41.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,你说了"和"这个词\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You used the word "and."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.95,0:08:44.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,莱茨和温妮今早去了市场部署\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Lights and Winnie set up in the Market this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.45,0:08:45.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们分布在各车厢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're spread out all over,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.12,0:08:47.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,但我们的人需要回来这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but our people need to be back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:50.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  但我得回去工作了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm sorry, but I have to get back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.46,0:08:52.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,-放心  我们没事的  -好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- It's all good. We cool. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.42,0:08:57.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,兄弟们  你们有什么想法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, boys, what you reckon?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.42,0:08:58.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们得去前车把所有人带回来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, we've gotta go uptrain and get everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.92,0:09:00.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,确保他们平安回家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Make sure they get back home safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.26,0:09:01.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.55,0:09:02.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,但他不能去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But not him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.22,0:09:04.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,他太引人注意了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He sticks out like a sore thumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.01,0:09:06.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,大力士可以留在这\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Strong Boy can hold it down back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.47,0:09:08.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,和\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.39,0:09:09.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,那派克呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What about Pike?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.06,0:09:12.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,派克是怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What is it with Pike, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.81,0:09:14.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,你不想知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ah, you don't wanna know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.73,0:09:17.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想只有你和我了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I think just you and me, mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.05,0:09:43.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们一会去车尾集合\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, we're gonna gather back in the Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.77,0:09:51.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,是你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.10,0:09:53.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.90,0:09:55.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们不想惹麻烦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}we don't want any trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.52,0:10:00.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,你杀了我的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You killed my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.07,0:10:02.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,现在轮到我杀你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And now, I kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.88,0:10:24.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,别让他出来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Don't let him back out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.64,0:10:26.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们一开始就不该\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We shouldn't have left the pastor
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.85,0:10:28.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,让牧师看着他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to watch over him in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.56,0:10:30.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,萨姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.39,0:10:33.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,你有多担心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How worried are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.52,0:10:37.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,每次你叫我名字时我都很担心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm always worried when you start using my first name.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.90,0:10:39.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,你在想什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's on your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.19,0:10:43.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,昨晚奥德丽和威尔福德先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}When Audrey and Mr. Wilford turned back
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.99,0:10:45.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,在边境回头时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}at the border last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.45,0:10:50.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,他让我去大爱丽丝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He asked me to step over onto Big Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.45,0:10:53.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,但你还在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, you're still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.75,0:10:56.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道该怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Didn't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.46,0:10:59.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,曾经的我一定会过去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There was a time that I would have.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.09,0:11:02.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,现在你不确定了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now you're not so sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.55,0:11:06.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,我效忠雪国列车  和你一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I serve Snowpiercer, just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.43,0:11:11.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,有七年时间我们曾井然有序\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We had order for seven years.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.10,0:11:14.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,我知道下令的是梅兰妮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know it was Melanie,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.02,0:11:15.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,但那些是他的规矩  不是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but they were his rules, weren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.73,0:11:17.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的  我们曾经井然有序\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, we had order.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:19.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,你还想干那种工作吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You want to do that job again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.65,0:11:21.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,冻掉他人的手臂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Taking arms?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.94,0:11:23.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,在车后侧管理集中营\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Running a gulag at the back of the train?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.33,0:11:31.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.37,0:11:36.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,为什么都交给你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So why's it all on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:38.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,莱顿已经够忙的了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, Layton has enough to deal with.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.67,0:11:41.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,这些人那么怪罪车尾人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All these people pointing fingers at Tailies,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.29,0:11:42.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,按说他会想对此做点什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you'd think he'd want to do something about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.80,0:11:43.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,他有的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.55,0:11:46.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,他交给我  去搞定这事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Trusting me to, uh, you know, get it done.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.05,0:11:46.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,而我...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.93,0:11:48.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,你想证明自己\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You want to prove yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.76,0:11:52.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,八个维修队的人  都在同一时间被谋杀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Eight Breachmen, all murdered at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.85,0:11:55.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,那就是八个愿意为威尔福德杀人的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's eight people willing to kill for Wilford.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.89,0:11:59.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,威尔福德无形的手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ah, the invisible hand of Wilford.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.44,0:12:01.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是真的  相信我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, it exists, believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.36,0:12:03.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,他在这安排了人幕后操纵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's got someone here pulling the strings.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.37,0:12:11.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,进来  进来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Eh, hey, come, come.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.70,0:12:13.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,下午好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.20,0:12:15.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,她不说英语\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Uh--she don't speak English.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.34,0:12:26.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,她想知道你们在找什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sh--she want to know what you look for.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.26,0:12:27.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,衣服  帽子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Clothes? Hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.17,0:12:29.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,你告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.35,0:12:41.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,她说扣子是夹克上的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She say button come from jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.90,0:12:45.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,怎么有这么多威尔福德的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's with all this Wilford stuff, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.15,0:12:48.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,祖母认识威尔福德先生很久了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Grandmother know Mr. Wilford for long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.65,0:12:51.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,她以前在谢菲尔德是他邻居\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She was neighbor in Sheffield.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.37,0:12:53.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,待他如自己侄子  她说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Like a nephew, she says.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.03,0:12:56.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,她带他去公园  教堂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She take him to park, to chapel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.70,0:12:59.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,她说他喜欢教堂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She say he love chapel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.12,0:13:02.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,他会在玻璃窗里点亮红色的蜡烛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He light red candle in glass window.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.88,0:13:05.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,这些红色小灯笼就是这个意思  对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, is that what all these little red lanterns are about, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.55,0:13:09.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,祖母让我每天都点  当作守夜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Grandmother ask me to light each day as vigil
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.26,0:13:11.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,直到威尔福德先生回来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}until Mr. Wilford return.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.34,0:13:12.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们也会给顾客\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We give them to customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.68,0:13:14.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们也替他点亮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They light it for him also.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.44,0:13:22.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,这衣服所有扣子都在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All the buttons are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.98,0:13:25.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是一套衣服中的一件吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Is this part of a set?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.73,0:13:28.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Da.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.20,0:13:33.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,没错  姊妹夹克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ah, yes, sister jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.41,0:13:36.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,祖母上周换掉了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Grandmother trade last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.91,0:13:38.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,换了个毛绒帽子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}For fur hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.16,0:13:39.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,你还记得她和谁换了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you remember who she traded with?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.66,0:13:41.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,一个美丽的女人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, beautiful woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.04,0:13:44.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,光鲜得像头等厢乘客\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Fancy like First Class.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.13,0:13:46.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,很高\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Very tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.64,0:14:00.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,雪国列车的公民\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Citizens of Snowpiercer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.48,0:14:04.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,今天我们为维修队的人默哀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Today, we are all in mourning for our Breachmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.81,0:14:06.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们害怕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We are afraid...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.56,0:14:09.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,因为我们中有人想要我们害怕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}because there are those among us who want us to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.57,0:14:13.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,这次暴力是精心策划用来离间我们的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This violence was orchestrated to divide us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.61,0:14:15.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,-让我们受损  -是车尾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- To compromise us... - It was the Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.95,0:14:17.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,通过除掉我们中最优秀的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}By taking out our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.37,0:14:20.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们不能反目成仇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We can't start turning on each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.87,0:14:23.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,否则就正中了他们的下怀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's exactly what they want to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.25,0:14:27.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,无论是谁犯下这可怕的罪行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Whoever did this terrible crime
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.54,0:14:29.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们想让你们认为始作俑者是我们中的弱者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}wants you to believe that it was the weakest among us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.51,0:14:31.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,胡说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.92,0:14:33.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,莱顿以前就是车尾人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Layton was a Tailie!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.09,0:14:38.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,真正的敌人在大爱丽丝上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The real enemy is back there on Big Alice,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.55,0:14:39.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,伺机静候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}lying in wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.22,0:14:42.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,你们的有些邻居支持他回归\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Some of your neighbors support his return,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.85,0:14:45.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,但我们已经摒弃了《威尔福德法》\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but we cast away Wilford Law once already.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.85,0:14:49.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,我提醒各位团结大家的信念\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And I will remind you of the call that unites us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.28,0:14:53.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们列车一心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We are one train.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.03,0:14:55.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,雪国列车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Snowpiercer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.61,0:14:57.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们为之奋斗的不是这个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is not what we fought for.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.84,0:15:16.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不确定他们会以你想要的方式去理解\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm not sure they'll take that the way you want them to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.47,0:15:17.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,我必须要为车尾辩护\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I had to defend the Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.09,0:15:19.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们现在还没有发声的途径\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They don't have a voice right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.93,0:15:21.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,把威尔福德先生牵扯进来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Bringing Mr. Wilford into it,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.22,0:15:22.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,你这是要他们站边\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you're asking them to pick sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.85,0:15:23.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,他必须要做点什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He had to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.44,0:15:29.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,那么  请务必  继续吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, then, by all means, carry on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.82,0:15:35.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,她也许是对的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She might be right, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.57,0:15:38.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们都知道这只是刚刚开始\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We both know this is just the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.74,0:15:43.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,我留下来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I stayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.58,0:15:45.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,这不是你想要的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Isn't that what you wanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.79,0:15:47.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想要你在我身边  奥德丽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I want you with me, Audrey.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.29,0:15:48.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,真心的在我身边\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Really with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.54,0:15:52.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,我没法一个人做这事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I can't do it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.88,0:15:55.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,那么  就像我相信你一样相信我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, then trust me like I'm trusting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.05,0:15:57.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想我应该得清楚我陷入了什么样的处境\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I think I should know what I've gotten myself into.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.97,0:16:01.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,你想要摊开了说话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You want all our cards on the table?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.14,0:16:03.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.86,0:16:13.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,我在你洗澡的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I found this screwdriver in your things
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.86,0:16:15.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,在你的衣物里发现了这个螺丝刀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}while you were taking a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.20,0:16:18.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,你要告诉我这是干什么用的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You want to tell me what it's for?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.03,0:16:23.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想你知道那是干什么用的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I think you know what it's for.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.08,0:16:26.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,对调通讯线\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Swap the comm lines
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.25,0:16:28.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,这样雪国列车就可以监听我的火车头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}so Snowpiercer can listen in on my Engine?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.75,0:16:30.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,你这么做了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Did you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.33,0:16:32.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.21,0:16:35.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,你留下来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Did you stay here
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.05,0:16:37.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,是为了完成你那个小任务吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}so you could complete your little mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.64,0:16:41.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,不是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.72,0:16:46.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,我留下来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I stayed...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.89,0:16:49.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,是因为我感受到了一股引力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}because I feel a pull.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.02,0:16:50.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,就在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.36,0:16:55.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,但是经过你对我所做的一切...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But after everything you've done to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.82,0:16:58.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白这种感觉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.40,0:16:59.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,但是我仍在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But I'm still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.99,0:17:05.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不相信你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.95,0:17:07.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,穿好衣服\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Get dressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.41,0:17:09.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想让你见个人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's someone I want you to meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:20.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,-我们要去哪  -你会知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Where are we going? - Oh, you'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.05,0:17:22.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,你必须要证明自己\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're going to have to prove yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.97,0:17:24.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,和其他人一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}like everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.68,0:17:27.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,约瑟夫  这是怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Joseph, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.43,0:17:33.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,我队伍里的这个可怜人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You see, this poor, poor member of my crew
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.81,0:17:35.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,已经完全崩溃了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}has gone all to pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.52,0:17:37.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,他需要你的帮助\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He needs your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.33,0:17:48.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  不要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No. No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.37,0:17:51.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  快走开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, no! Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.16,0:17:55.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,别管我  不  快走开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Leave me alone! No! Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.33,0:17:58.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,快走开  别管我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Leave me alone! Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.84,0:17:59.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.13,0:18:01.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,不要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.84,0:18:03.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,请别这样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Please, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.97,0:18:07.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,这位是凯文\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is Kevin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.77,0:18:11.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,-不  -我要你治好他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- No! - I need you to fix him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.48,0:18:27.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,莱顿的革命本应该是为了我们所有人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Layton's revolution was supposed to be for all of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.02,0:18:28.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,去他妈的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}To hell with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.10,0:18:30.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,一朝车尾人  永远都是车尾人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Once a Tailie, always a Tailie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.02,0:18:31.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是威尔福德的列车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is Wilford's train!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.40,0:18:33.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,以前一直是  以后永远也是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Always was, always will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.11,0:18:35.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们去干掉几个车尾人吧  走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let's get some Tailies! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.44,0:18:37.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,天呐  莱顿现在是骑虎难下了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, man, Layton's in for it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.50,0:18:48.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,派克  你还好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Pike? You good?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.46,0:18:50.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,莱顿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Layton.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.63,0:18:53.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,我的老哥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.71,0:18:55.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,我很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.17,0:18:57.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,你确定吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.01,0:18:58.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,你看上去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}'Cause you don't, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.47,0:19:00.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,看上去不太好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you don't look so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.10,0:19:06.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,特伦斯那事并没有如计划那般  但是...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thing with Terence didn't quite go as planned, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.52,0:19:12.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,我很欣慰  现在你欠我人情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I take comfort in knowing that you now owe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.44,0:19:17.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,没错  有我为你撑腰呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, hey. I got your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.03,0:19:19.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么不现在回到车尾呢  好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, um, why don't you head back to the Tail, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.57,0:19:20.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,-外面很危险  -没事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- It's dangerous out here. - Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.99,0:19:21.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,我没事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.41,0:19:23.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,你现在是个靶子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're a target.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.62,0:19:26.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,我这个样子没人能认出来  莱顿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nobody recognizes me like this, Layton.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.04,0:19:26.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.25,0:19:30.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,我查了总账\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I-I checked the ledger.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.13,0:19:33.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,计算了数字\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I did the figures.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.42,0:19:37.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,我证实了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And I have proven...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.47,0:19:41.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,现在  天平其实\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that the scale is actually
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.84,0:19:44.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,更偏向派克一点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}now a little more in Pike's favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.56,0:19:47.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,我计算了你欠的债\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I counted your debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.52,0:19:51.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,你现在已经被标记了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You are now marked.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.96,0:20:08.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,这边  这边  低调点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, hey, hey. It's this way. This way. Lay low.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.71,0:20:14.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,他还好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Is he okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.75,0:20:17.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想我让他有了心理创伤\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I think I messed him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.42,0:20:22.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,来  你可以扭转局面的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come on. You can turn this around.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.43,0:20:26.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,你在这呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.47,0:20:27.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,你去哪了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Where were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.27,0:20:31.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,奥德丽在帮我做点事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Audrey's helping me with something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.52,0:20:32.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,做什么事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}With what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.32,0:20:35.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,一个小项目\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Little project.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.81,0:20:36.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,到时你就知道了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You'll see.
