Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.24,0:38:32.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,我给了他一些空间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I...gave him some space.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.92,0:38:33.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,去哀悼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}To grieve.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.63,0:38:36.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,出什么事了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.19,0:38:38.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,那都是在演戏吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Is it all an act?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.26,0:38:40.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.45,0:38:41.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,茶杯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The teacup.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.43,0:38:44.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,灵性\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The spirituality.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.30,0:38:47.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,都是扯淡  对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's all bullshit, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.41,0:38:50.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,你在给威尔福德卖命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're the one working for Wilford.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.95,0:38:52.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,-别管  -贝丝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Leave it. - Bess.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.42,0:38:53.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,别骗我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Don't lie to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.26,0:38:54.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,我从没骗过你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I never lied to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.38,0:38:59.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,你只是没准备好倾听\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You just weren't ready to listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.85,0:39:01.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,这么久以来你一直在利用我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Were you just using me all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.58,0:39:04.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,你内心的怒火  我也能感觉到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That rage inside of you, I feel it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.21,0:39:05.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,你不了解我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You don't know me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.05,0:39:07.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,你渴望能抓住什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You were so desperate for something to hold onto.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.04,0:39:08.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,相信什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Something to believe in.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.53,0:39:09.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想帮你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I wanted to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.02,0:39:11.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,你杀了八个人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You killed eight people.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.99,0:39:15.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,这是换取和平的一个小代价而已\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A small price to pay for peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.34,0:39:17.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,你不觉得吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.85,0:39:27.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.26,0:39:28.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,-不  -放他走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- No! - Let him go!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.45,0:39:30.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,-放他走  -我们不要再听你的了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Let him go! - We are done listening to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.54,0:39:31.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,等等  杰克斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Wait--Jakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.58,0:39:33.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,杰克斯  我认识你  你为什么要这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jakes, I know you. Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.41,0:39:35.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,-我们一起抗争过  -那是个错误\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- We--we fought together! - That was a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.43,0:39:36.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,就不该让你离开车尾的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Never should've let you out of the Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.95,0:39:38.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,-叛徒  叛徒  -嘿  嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Traitors! Traitors! - Hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.33,0:39:39.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,够了  够了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, stop it! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.68,0:39:41.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,你要想惩罚谁的话  拿走我的手臂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You wanna punish somebody, take my arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.78,0:39:44.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,拿走我的手臂  放掉派克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Take my arm. Let Pike go.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.33,0:39:46.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,-他疯了  -不可能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Hey, he's crazy, man. - No. No way, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.57,0:39:47.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,-不不  -嘿  嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- No, no. No! - Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.88,0:39:49.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,你们想要的是我  对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I am the one you want, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.09,0:39:52.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,-你们恨的人是我  -安德烈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- I'm the one you hate. - Andre...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.34,0:39:55.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,我夺走了你们的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I took everything that you had,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.93,0:39:57.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,然后我给了我朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and I gave it to my friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.15,0:39:59.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以带走我  拿走我的手臂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So take me. Here. Arm me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.14,0:40:00.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,来啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.35,0:40:03.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No! No! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.78,0:40:06.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.48,0:40:09.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.30,0:40:12.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  等等\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.46,0:40:20.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,住手  住手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Stop it! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.71,0:40:22.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,这太野蛮了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is barbaric!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.15,0:40:24.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,这人是你们的领袖\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This man is your leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.60,0:40:26.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,你们选择了他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You chose him!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.78,0:40:28.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,你们想要别人来领导\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You want someone else in charge,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.09,0:40:29.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,那就号召改变\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}then call for change.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.35,0:40:33.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,但别因为你们可以\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But don't strip him down and mutilate him
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.56,0:40:34.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,就剥下他衣服  让他残废\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}just because you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.56,0:40:36.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,这样不对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.24,0:40:39.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,相信我  我了解的  我这么做过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Believe me, I know. I've done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.95,0:40:44.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,你们再也变回不了曾经的样子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You'll never be the same again once you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.20,0:40:47.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,这不是办法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is not the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.37,0:40:49.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,不再是了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.16,0:40:53.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,-拜托  -司闸员要来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Please. - The Brakemen are coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.86,0:40:54.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们得走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We gotta go!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.89,0:40:57.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,这事没完\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This ain't over.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.80,0:41:01.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,滚吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, piss off!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.18,0:41:03.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let's get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.63,0:41:04.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,快点  快点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come on, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.36,0:41:08.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,你注意点  派克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Watch yourself, Pike.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.92,0:41:17.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们都想要稳定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We all crave stability.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.53,0:41:20.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,但威尔福德能带来秩序\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But Wilford brings order.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.15,0:41:24.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须受苦一小会儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We just have to suffer for a moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.87,0:41:26.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,才能得到救赎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to get to our salvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.32,0:41:31.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,没有伤害你就找不到解脱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You can't find relief without...hurting.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.79,0:41:46.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,动手吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.44,0:41:50.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不会杀了你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I am not going to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.74,0:41:53.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,你要是死了  就没人知道真相了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If you die, no one learns the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.87,0:42:16.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,我向你祈祷\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I pray to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.64,0:42:19.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,我向你祈祷  我汲取力量\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I pray to you, and I draw strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.79,0:42:23.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,欢庆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Rejoice.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.98,0:42:45.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.26,0:42:47.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.89,0:43:24.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.81,0:43:26.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,我错过了螺丝锥吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Did I miss the corkscrew?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.74,0:43:27.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,没有  过来坐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No. Come sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.64,0:43:50.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们在选边  艾莉克斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They're choosing sides, Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.12,0:43:54.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,跟我来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.69,0:44:11.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.68,0:44:16.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们在召唤你  约瑟夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They're calling for you, Joseph.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.82,0:44:30.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,列车想要威尔福德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The train wants Wilford.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.74,0:44:38.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们要点燃一根吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Should we light one?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.14,0:44:43.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,我还不确定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm not sure yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.27,0:44:48.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,安德烈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Andre?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.92,0:45:17.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,叫海德伍德夫妇准备冷淡鲍勃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Tell the Headwoods to prep Icy Bob.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.65,0:45:19.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,是时候了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's time.
